1
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:07,920
[A Prime Minister's Disguise]

2
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:10,870
[Episode 23]

3
00:01:17,250 --> 00:01:18,850
From field to table.

4
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:20,250
Green and healthy.

5
00:01:20,289 --> 00:01:22,450
Little Heng No. 46 is served.

6
00:01:26,450 --> 00:01:27,630
What's No. 46?

7
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,289
Try it.

8
00:01:29,380 --> 00:01:30,580
Your Majesty may not know,

9
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:31,690
the old general

10
00:01:31,730 --> 00:01:32,530
grows attached to

11
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:33,440
everything he raises.

12
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,090
So,

13
00:01:34,410 --> 00:01:35,740
he named it Little Heng.

14
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:37,820
Your Majesty, please try it.

15
00:01:40,670 --> 00:01:41,130
How is it?

16
00:01:41,130 --> 00:01:41,890
Is it tender this time?

17
00:01:41,890 --> 00:01:42,950
Tastes good today.

18
00:01:42,970 --> 00:01:43,920
Haha!

19
00:01:44,570 --> 00:01:45,970
The chickens that run in the wild

20
00:01:45,970 --> 00:01:47,500
really do nourish the body.

21
00:01:48,850 --> 00:01:49,729
Look at me,

22
00:01:49,770 --> 00:01:50,590
isn't I in much better spirits

23
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:51,850
than I were a couple of years ago?

24
00:01:51,850 --> 00:01:52,289
Yes,

25
00:01:52,289 --> 00:01:53,050
indeed.

26
00:01:53,250 --> 00:01:54,890
Hahaha.

27
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:58,050
Grandfather,

28
00:01:58,370 --> 00:02:00,450
this time it's truly urgent.

29
00:02:01,370 --> 00:02:02,130
That's why,

30
00:02:02,370 --> 00:02:04,170
as Emperor, I've come to ask for your help.

31
00:02:04,170 --> 00:02:04,890
What?

32
00:02:05,170 --> 00:02:06,090
You dare to call yourself Emperor

33
00:02:06,090 --> 00:02:07,170
in front of me?

34
00:02:07,730 --> 00:02:08,250
General, General,

35
00:02:08,250 --> 00:02:08,690
sit down.

36
00:02:08,690 --> 00:02:09,490
Sit down.

37
00:02:12,090 --> 00:02:13,490
I was wrong.

38
00:02:13,890 --> 00:02:14,450
I...

39
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:17,329
Mobilizing troops from the capital

40
00:02:17,380 --> 00:02:18,990
is not only a waste of resources,

41
00:02:18,990 --> 00:02:19,930
but the casualties

42
00:02:19,930 --> 00:02:21,310
will surely be severe.

43
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,090
If you return to lead,

44
00:02:23,810 --> 00:02:25,740
we can certainly defeat the enemy!

45
00:02:27,610 --> 00:02:29,210
Don't waste your words.

46
00:02:29,210 --> 00:02:31,250
I've said it before,

47
00:02:31,350 --> 00:02:32,650
you're just a reckless martial arts practitioner.

48
00:02:32,650 --> 00:02:33,810
But you insist on overestimating yourself,

49
00:02:33,810 --> 00:02:35,090
wanting to be the emperor.

50
00:02:35,090 --> 00:02:35,740
Yes.

51
00:02:42,329 --> 00:02:43,370
Now it's good.

52
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:44,370
Stay here

53
00:02:44,410 --> 00:02:47,210
and keep me company raising chickens and farming.

54
00:02:48,010 --> 00:02:48,500
Guards!

55
00:02:48,930 --> 00:02:49,690
Yes, General.

56
00:02:49,690 --> 00:02:50,850
Take him to the pigsty,

57
00:02:50,850 --> 00:02:52,579
and teach him how to raise pigs.

58
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,250
Your Majesty,

59
00:02:53,250 --> 00:02:53,530
please.

60
00:02:53,530 --> 00:02:55,390
Let me teach you how to raise pigs.

61
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:57,730
Put down your sword!

62
00:02:57,730 --> 00:02:58,530
Grandfather,

63
00:02:58,530 --> 00:02:59,810
I still respectfully address you as

64
00:02:59,810 --> 00:03:00,810
General Du.

65
00:03:01,340 --> 00:03:02,210
You're angry at me for

66
00:03:02,210 --> 00:03:03,490
being presumptuous back then,

67
00:03:03,490 --> 00:03:05,610
for insisting on becoming the emperor.

68
00:03:05,610 --> 00:03:07,340
But I did it for only one reason.

69
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,370
I wish for peace in this world.

70
00:03:09,770 --> 00:03:11,430
Now that the enemy has invaded,

71
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,930
for the state and the people,

72
00:03:12,930 --> 00:03:13,930
for those who once fought

73
00:03:13,930 --> 00:03:14,890
side by side with me,

74
00:03:14,890 --> 00:03:16,090
my trusted advisors,

75
00:03:16,650 --> 00:03:17,930
I beg you to return.

76
00:03:26,370 --> 00:03:28,140
That reckless boy

77
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,890
has indeed grown up.

78
00:03:31,329 --> 00:03:32,690
It seems my daughter

79
00:03:32,690 --> 00:03:34,200
has raised her son well.

80
00:03:35,410 --> 00:03:36,130
However,

81
00:03:37,410 --> 00:03:38,210
I won't

82
00:03:38,530 --> 00:03:40,090
send troops!

83
00:03:40,170 --> 00:03:41,230
Grandfather, you—

84
00:03:42,490 --> 00:03:43,410
You little rascal.

85
00:03:43,410 --> 00:03:44,250
How dare you put a sword

86
00:03:44,250 --> 00:03:45,090
to your uncle's throat?

87
00:03:45,090 --> 00:03:45,690
It's fine.

88
00:03:46,610 --> 00:03:47,690
His Majesty is just joking with me.

89
00:03:47,690 --> 00:03:48,250
I was wrong.

90
00:03:48,250 --> 00:03:49,780
General, please calm down.

91
00:03:59,329 --> 00:04:00,460
We're almost there.

92
00:04:01,050 --> 00:04:02,250
Keep moving forward.

93
00:04:03,450 --> 00:04:04,730
Yes, Your Highness.

94
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:14,450
He is a traitor.

95
00:04:14,450 --> 00:04:15,250
Where's the evidence?

96
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:16,450
I will find it.

97
00:04:20,230 --> 00:04:20,990
Stop.

98
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:22,290
Make them all stop.

99
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:23,170
Hyah!

100
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,390
Whoa!

101
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:33,420
Seems Your Highness doesn't trust me anymore.

102
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:34,409
Huo Jingheng

103
00:04:34,620 --> 00:04:36,530
has reached the Northwest Army's position.

104
00:04:36,530 --> 00:04:37,450
Yue Chi,

105
00:04:37,690 --> 00:04:39,290
I did trust you.

106
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,450
But the Princess told me...

107
00:04:42,409 --> 00:04:44,140
Do you really plan to move east?

108
00:04:44,940 --> 00:04:45,820
Why not?

109
00:04:46,420 --> 00:04:47,790
Once renowned throughout the land,

110
00:04:47,790 --> 00:04:49,790
General Du, the leader of the Northwest Army,

111
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:49,890
[Mount Fengming]

112
00:04:49,890 --> 00:04:51,490
is now living in Mount Fengming.

113
00:04:51,490 --> 00:04:52,170
If the Li's army moves east,

114
00:04:52,170 --> 00:04:53,770
we'll certainly pass there.

115
00:04:54,170 --> 00:04:54,850
That day,

116
00:04:54,890 --> 00:04:55,600
I overheard

117
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:56,960
Yue Chi and someone

118
00:04:56,990 --> 00:04:58,310
having a secret conversation in the army.

119
00:04:58,310 --> 00:04:59,440
Who else do you think

120
00:04:59,770 --> 00:05:00,890
could risk coming alone

121
00:05:00,890 --> 00:05:02,270
to the Li's army camp,

122
00:05:02,290 --> 00:05:04,330
and also persuade General Du

123
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:05,350
to come out?

124
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,450
She knows you best.

125
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:08,610
I had to

126
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:10,250
consider her words.

127
00:05:10,450 --> 00:05:11,970
You've disappointed me.

128
00:05:26,930 --> 00:05:27,730
Yue Chi,

129
00:05:28,210 --> 00:05:29,810
why won't you join me?

130
00:05:30,010 --> 00:05:31,740
We are clearly on the same path.

131
00:05:31,770 --> 00:05:33,170
You're mistaken.

132
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:36,140
We've never been on the same path.

133
00:05:37,210 --> 00:05:39,130
I've long had my own companions.

134
00:05:43,770 --> 00:05:44,730
Take him away.

135
00:05:45,770 --> 00:05:46,620
Seems I was never meant to walk

136
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:48,080
the same path with Yue Chi.

137
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:48,710
So be it.

138
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:49,930
Go back,

139
00:05:50,250 --> 00:05:51,330
set the trap,

140
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,530
and prepare to welcome our guests.

141
00:05:54,090 --> 00:05:55,330
I'll go prepare.

142
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:56,850
Xue Jingguan.

143
00:05:57,409 --> 00:05:58,409
As for Yue Chi,

144
00:05:59,010 --> 00:06:01,070
do you want to deal with him yourself?

145
00:06:02,740 --> 00:06:05,600
Your Highness, please dispose of him as you see fit.

146
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:06,770
I will kill him.

147
00:06:10,130 --> 00:06:11,860
Don't you have anything to say?

148
00:06:12,450 --> 00:06:13,580
Just a bit of regret.

149
00:06:15,010 --> 00:06:15,890
But

150
00:06:16,530 --> 00:06:18,590
what does Your Highness want to hear?

151
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:29,780
I'm sorry,

152
00:06:29,810 --> 00:06:30,490
Yue Chi.

153
00:06:31,610 --> 00:06:32,780
Fate has given me

154
00:06:32,810 --> 00:06:34,070
gifts I don't deserve.

155
00:06:34,370 --> 00:06:35,970
I can only accept one.

156
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:56,409
Don't choose me in the next life.

157
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:10,330
I've searched.

158
00:07:10,610 --> 00:07:13,010
There's nothing to eat or drink over there.

159
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:14,050
Are you sure

160
00:07:14,050 --> 00:07:15,090
that crossing

161
00:07:15,450 --> 00:07:17,170
gets us to Li's camp?

162
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:22,630
I'm about 80% certain.

163
00:07:28,050 --> 00:07:29,570
Worth a shot.

164
00:07:30,780 --> 00:07:31,730
From here on,

165
00:07:32,530 --> 00:07:33,650
I must go alone.

166
00:07:34,330 --> 00:07:35,590
You should hurry back.

167
00:07:36,050 --> 00:07:37,010
No way.

168
00:07:37,650 --> 00:07:39,380
We're almost at the final step.

169
00:07:39,730 --> 00:07:40,650
I can't leave you

170
00:07:40,650 --> 00:07:41,850
to face danger alone.

171
00:07:42,110 --> 00:07:43,010
Two people facing danger

172
00:07:43,010 --> 00:07:44,170
is still danger.

173
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:47,760
Du Tianzhao,

174
00:07:48,650 --> 00:07:50,460
I'm truly grateful to you.

175
00:07:51,850 --> 00:07:53,310
You've come so far with me.

176
00:07:55,130 --> 00:07:56,130
I'm the Imperial Uncle.

177
00:07:56,130 --> 00:07:57,250
Consort Yue and I are both here.

178
00:07:57,250 --> 00:07:58,450
Who dares make a move?

179
00:08:15,410 --> 00:08:16,410
Enough.

180
00:08:17,310 --> 00:08:18,330
That's enough.

181
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:23,690
I, Yue Ling'er,

182
00:08:23,690 --> 00:08:25,420
will remember this in my heart.

183
00:08:30,610 --> 00:08:31,410
Ling'er,

184
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,210
there's something

185
00:08:33,580 --> 00:08:35,530
I've kept in my heart for a long time.

186
00:08:35,530 --> 00:08:37,010
I want to tell you today.

187
00:08:39,210 --> 00:08:41,140
Ac... actually, I've always known

188
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:42,520
that you don't like me.

189
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,810
But

190
00:08:45,170 --> 00:08:46,770
even if it's just as a friend,

191
00:08:46,990 --> 00:08:48,520
I still want to walk with you

192
00:08:49,060 --> 00:08:50,860
on this long and difficult road.

193
00:08:51,570 --> 00:08:52,900
This isn't just for you,

194
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:54,580
it's more for myself.

195
00:08:55,650 --> 00:08:56,930
For the person I love,

196
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,730
for the life I want,

197
00:09:00,450 --> 00:09:02,380
I, Du Tianzhao, have fought for it.

198
00:09:06,610 --> 00:09:07,730
Du Tianzhao.

199
00:09:10,740 --> 00:09:11,850
Go quickly.

200
00:09:12,290 --> 00:09:13,890
The road ahead is still long.

201
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:32,850
Ling'er, no one's here.

202
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,610
I wonder

203
00:09:42,770 --> 00:09:44,210
what that Prime Minister Yue

204
00:09:44,210 --> 00:09:45,410
is really after.

205
00:09:45,990 --> 00:09:46,850
Who would've thought

206
00:09:46,850 --> 00:09:48,170
he was a spy all along?

207
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:49,690
Now look—

208
00:09:49,850 --> 00:09:51,210
I heard they're not even

209
00:09:51,250 --> 00:09:52,650
giving him food or water.

210
00:09:53,050 --> 00:09:53,650
Let's go.

211
00:09:53,690 --> 00:09:55,090
Let's get some food from the kitchen.

212
00:09:55,090 --> 00:09:55,970
Let's go.

213
00:10:23,110 --> 00:10:25,240
Your sleeping incense really worked.

214
00:10:25,410 --> 00:10:26,210
Of course.

215
00:10:26,250 --> 00:10:27,930
I had Yingwan specially make it.

216
00:10:27,930 --> 00:10:30,060
It's more potent than other incenses.

217
00:10:34,850 --> 00:10:35,610
Chi.

218
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:37,010
Ling'er.

219
00:10:45,770 --> 00:10:46,700
Are you alright?

220
00:10:47,770 --> 00:10:49,230
Why have you gotten so dark

221
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,530
and lost so much weight?

222
00:10:50,530 --> 00:10:51,170
Never mind

223
00:10:51,170 --> 00:10:52,210
how we got here.

224
00:10:52,380 --> 00:10:53,170
The soldiers outside

225
00:10:53,170 --> 00:10:54,120
have already been knocked out,

226
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,370
but it won't last long.

227
00:10:55,370 --> 00:10:56,130
We need to

228
00:10:56,170 --> 00:10:57,570
get you out of here first.

229
00:11:01,050 --> 00:11:02,610
How do we unlock this?

230
00:11:03,170 --> 00:11:04,570
This is no ordinary lock.

231
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,250
Looks like it's based on a Tibetan

232
00:11:06,250 --> 00:11:07,650
Vajra Blossom lock.

233
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:09,330
We need the right tool

234
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,970
and enough force

235
00:11:11,010 --> 00:11:12,050
to open it.

236
00:11:13,050 --> 00:11:13,920
Ling'er,

237
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,400
don't worry about me.

238
00:11:16,490 --> 00:11:18,050
This lock won't open.

239
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,200
We need to find a way

240
00:11:19,610 --> 00:11:20,730
to send someone up the mountain

241
00:11:20,730 --> 00:11:22,290
to the Northwest Army's camp

242
00:11:22,290 --> 00:11:23,490
and tell Huo Jingheng

243
00:11:23,570 --> 00:11:24,970
that the Li's Army
has seen through our plan

244
00:11:24,970 --> 00:11:26,570
and they haven't moved east.

245
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:30,850
Alright, I understand.

246
00:11:30,850 --> 00:11:31,910
I'll go right away.

247
00:11:32,490 --> 00:11:33,250
Ling'er.

248
00:11:35,610 --> 00:11:36,810
It's very dangerous.

249
00:11:36,810 --> 00:11:37,930
Be careful.

250
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:40,050
Don't worry.

251
00:11:40,690 --> 00:11:42,690
As long as I'm not shattered into pieces,

252
00:11:42,690 --> 00:11:43,570
I'll make sure

253
00:11:43,570 --> 00:11:45,230
Ling'er stays safe and sound.

254
00:11:48,350 --> 00:11:49,480
I'm counting on you.

255
00:12:02,170 --> 00:12:03,430
Be careful on your way.

256
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:09,960
Let's go, Ling'er.

257
00:12:21,430 --> 00:12:22,330
Your Highness,

258
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:24,090
there's a man and a woman
acting suspicious

259
00:12:24,090 --> 00:12:25,170
outside the camp.

260
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:29,770
Be careful.

261
00:12:29,890 --> 00:12:31,020
It's very slippery.

262
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:32,650
I knew

263
00:12:33,450 --> 00:12:34,250
my brother and His Majesty

264
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,850
wouldn't fall out so easily.

265
00:12:37,770 --> 00:12:38,690
It's just that

266
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:41,210
they're keeping things from me again.

267
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:43,460
Well, going all out with the act.

268
00:12:43,570 --> 00:12:45,370
Aren't they keeping things from me too?

269
00:12:45,370 --> 00:12:46,210
But

270
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,410
come to think of it,

271
00:12:47,690 --> 00:12:48,330
they

272
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:49,980
still have to rely on us,

273
00:12:50,010 --> 00:12:50,960
don't you think?

274
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:53,120
Mainly relying on you.

275
00:12:53,770 --> 00:12:55,140
So we need to

276
00:12:55,170 --> 00:12:57,100
put in more effort to move forward.

277
00:12:57,810 --> 00:12:59,410
That sister Yunqing of yours

278
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:01,290
is truly a vicious woman.

279
00:13:01,810 --> 00:13:03,090
Next time you see her,

280
00:13:03,130 --> 00:13:04,660
you won't go soft, will you?

281
00:13:09,810 --> 00:13:10,670
I won't go soft.

282
00:13:19,810 --> 00:13:20,490
You...

283
00:13:22,570 --> 00:13:23,550
Let her go.

284
00:13:30,770 --> 00:13:31,770
Let go of Ling'er!

285
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:34,440
You really think

286
00:13:34,450 --> 00:13:35,610
just the two of you

287
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,900
can make it to the Northwest Army's camp?

288
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:38,690
Without you,

289
00:13:38,690 --> 00:13:39,890
I could make it there.

290
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:41,250
Without me,

291
00:13:41,530 --> 00:13:43,440
could you even get out of this swamp

292
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,640
and make it through this miasma forest?

293
00:13:49,130 --> 00:13:50,170
Let go of me first.

294
00:13:50,970 --> 00:13:52,090
I really don't know

295
00:13:52,210 --> 00:13:53,970
why you're always against us.

