588
00:28:39,930 --> 00:28:41,990
is willing to lead the Northwest Army

589
00:28:42,130 --> 00:28:43,730
to station at Mount Fengming

590
00:28:44,140 --> 00:28:46,570
and guard the border for Ning.

591
00:28:47,860 --> 00:28:48,920
It's getting late.

592
00:28:49,210 --> 00:28:50,210
Mount your horse.

593
00:28:55,450 --> 00:28:56,710
Take care of yourself.

594
00:29:04,210 --> 00:29:05,970
By His Majesty's verbal decree:

595
00:29:05,970 --> 00:29:08,010
Due to ongoing military affairs,

596
00:29:08,050 --> 00:29:09,250
His Majesty is unwell

597
00:29:09,450 --> 00:29:11,810
and won't attend morning court for the next few days.

598
00:29:11,810 --> 00:29:12,810
Court dismissed.

599
00:29:20,690 --> 00:29:21,470
[Auspice and Blessing]

600
00:29:21,470 --> 00:29:22,530
Your Majesty,

601
00:29:22,550 --> 00:29:23,570
as per your instructions,

602
00:29:23,570 --> 00:29:24,840
I have dismissed them all.

603
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:27,040
They were all quite angry.

604
00:29:28,390 --> 00:29:29,210
I see.

605
00:29:30,130 --> 00:29:31,450
You,

606
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:32,770
won the battle

607
00:29:33,420 --> 00:29:34,570
but lost Ling'er.

608
00:29:37,250 --> 00:29:38,110
Say something.

609
00:29:41,050 --> 00:29:42,930
Bring Ling'er back.

610
00:29:43,050 --> 00:29:45,410
Bring Ling'er back.

611
00:29:48,930 --> 00:29:53,030
[Auspice and Blessing]

612
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:00,450
Your Majesty.

613
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:07,620
[Auspice and Blessing]

614
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:16,810
I will definitely bring Ling'er

615
00:30:16,810 --> 00:30:17,610
back.

616
00:30:47,050 --> 00:30:48,170
I adore you.

617
00:30:49,250 --> 00:30:50,130
I like you.

618
00:30:50,970 --> 00:30:51,690
I want you

619
00:30:51,690 --> 00:30:53,250
to stay, not just today.

620
00:30:53,450 --> 00:30:54,690
Every day from now on,

621
00:30:55,410 --> 00:30:56,290
I hope you can

622
00:30:56,290 --> 00:30:57,370
stay by my side,

623
00:30:58,090 --> 00:31:00,010
to help me, to be with me.

624
00:31:00,850 --> 00:31:02,710
Not just as Emperor Huo Jingheng,

625
00:31:02,980 --> 00:31:03,850
but more as

626
00:31:03,890 --> 00:31:06,420
this man, Huo Jingheng, standing before you.

627
00:31:06,490 --> 00:31:07,430
Ling'er,

628
00:31:08,850 --> 00:31:09,850
will you?

629
00:31:12,250 --> 00:31:13,370
Wait here.

630
00:31:14,090 --> 00:31:15,150
Yes, Your Majesty.

631
00:32:08,180 --> 00:32:10,260
[Heng]

632
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:14,770
Your Majesty, you men always think

633
00:32:14,770 --> 00:32:16,370
you're meant

634
00:32:16,410 --> 00:32:17,270
to solve everything,

635
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:18,130
[Heng]

636
00:32:18,130 --> 00:32:19,450
and should fix

637
00:32:19,450 --> 00:32:20,650
more problems.

638
00:32:21,290 --> 00:32:22,490
But this time,

639
00:32:22,490 --> 00:32:24,250
how was it solved?

640
00:32:24,570 --> 00:32:26,300
Have you ever thought about it?

641
00:32:44,760 --> 00:32:46,370
Living so comfortably, huh?

642
00:32:47,420 --> 00:32:48,410
Of course.

643
00:32:56,690 --> 00:32:57,450
Ling'er,

644
00:32:58,010 --> 00:32:58,940
would you like to

645
00:32:59,330 --> 00:33:00,390
have a drink with me

646
00:33:01,280 --> 00:33:02,210
and then go to

647
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:04,320
Mount Wanting in the Imperial Garden

648
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:05,980
to watch the sunset together?

649
00:33:08,690 --> 00:33:09,730
With me?

650
00:33:10,140 --> 00:33:11,410
Today?

651
00:33:11,450 --> 00:33:12,450
No.

652
00:33:13,040 --> 00:33:15,380
With you, every day.

653
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:20,930
Who wants to be with you every day?

654
00:34:49,530 --> 00:34:50,989
Greetings, Your Majesty.

655
00:35:09,330 --> 00:35:10,090
Go,

656
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:12,160
bring a basin of water

657
00:35:12,770 --> 00:35:14,290
and fetch me some rags.

658
00:35:15,810 --> 00:35:16,730
Go now.

659
00:35:18,530 --> 00:35:19,690
Yes, Your Majesty.

660
00:35:48,690 --> 00:35:49,810
How could His Majesty

661
00:35:49,810 --> 00:35:51,090
do such chores?

662
00:35:51,330 --> 00:35:51,970
His Majesty

663
00:35:51,970 --> 00:35:53,850
misses Her Highness so much.

664
00:35:55,850 --> 00:35:56,850
Let's go help.

665
00:35:58,850 --> 00:36:00,380
Although he is the Emperor,

666
00:36:00,650 --> 00:36:01,490
he is also

667
00:36:01,490 --> 00:36:02,820
Consort Yue's husband.

668
00:36:03,610 --> 00:36:05,450
He just wants to tidy up the house

669
00:36:05,610 --> 00:36:07,470
and wait for his wife to come home.

670
00:36:51,050 --> 00:36:51,770
One!

671
00:36:53,370 --> 00:36:54,090
Two!

672
00:36:55,970 --> 00:36:56,690
Three.

673
00:36:57,010 --> 00:36:57,650
Your Majesty,

674
00:36:57,650 --> 00:36:59,000
the Li's army and the Kingdom Restoration League

675
00:36:59,000 --> 00:36:59,610
are attacking together,

676
00:36:59,610 --> 00:37:01,010
heading for the Ning-Li border.

677
00:37:01,010 --> 00:37:02,510
Quickly order the Northwest Army down the mountain.

678
00:37:02,510 --> 00:37:03,740
Hold the Ning-Li border at all costs.

679
00:37:03,740 --> 00:37:04,800
Yes, Your Majesty.

680
00:37:07,690 --> 00:37:08,860
Last time, they didn't choose

681
00:37:08,860 --> 00:37:10,210
to attack the Fengming Garrison.

682
00:37:10,210 --> 00:37:11,030
It's probably because

683
00:37:11,030 --> 00:37:11,750
the garrison has high walls

684
00:37:11,750 --> 00:37:12,810
and fortified towers,

685
00:37:12,810 --> 00:37:13,970
making it difficult to breach.

686
00:37:13,970 --> 00:37:15,890
So they retreated and opened fire on Mount Fengming instead.

687
00:37:15,890 --> 00:37:17,270
Unexpectedly, on Mount Fengming,

688
00:37:17,270 --> 00:37:18,090
there was a tough opponent.

689
00:37:18,090 --> 00:37:19,810
This time, they've gathered their forces.

690
00:37:19,810 --> 00:37:21,470
It seems they're going all in,

691
00:37:21,970 --> 00:37:23,300
coming well-prepared.

692
00:37:27,370 --> 00:37:28,190
Your Majesty,

693
00:37:28,770 --> 00:37:30,290
the military situation at the front is urgent.

694
00:37:30,290 --> 00:37:32,050
The Li State's army and the Kingdom Restoration League

695
00:37:32,050 --> 00:37:32,890
have formed an alliance.

696
00:37:32,890 --> 00:37:34,530
The Crown Prince of Li State is ambitious

697
00:37:34,530 --> 00:37:35,570
and has provoked us repeatedly,

698
00:37:35,570 --> 00:37:36,690
but always retreated in defeat.

699
00:37:36,690 --> 00:37:38,830
But this time, they've gathered

700
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:39,660
their forces.

701
00:37:39,690 --> 00:37:41,290
Even General Du's Northwest Army

702
00:37:41,290 --> 00:37:42,810
cannot hold out alone.

703
00:37:46,170 --> 00:37:46,990
Your Majesty,

704
00:37:47,410 --> 00:37:48,820
the two enemy armies have joined forces.

705
00:37:48,820 --> 00:37:50,420
We have already gathered all

706
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:51,490
our available troops.

707
00:37:51,490 --> 00:37:52,410
I request permission

708
00:37:52,410 --> 00:37:53,670
to personally lead

709
00:37:53,700 --> 00:37:55,480
the Qilin Army and join Ning's elite troops

710
00:37:55,480 --> 00:37:56,480
to march together

711
00:37:56,490 --> 00:37:57,670
and repel the enemy.

712
00:37:58,610 --> 00:37:59,500
Your Majesty,

713
00:38:00,290 --> 00:38:01,260
I disagree.

714
00:38:02,570 --> 00:38:03,850
If word spreads that

715
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:05,370
we're fighting alongside

716
00:38:05,390 --> 00:38:06,290
the previous dynasty's army,

717
00:38:06,290 --> 00:38:07,680
other nations will think

718
00:38:07,680 --> 00:38:09,900
that our Ning has no principles.

719
00:38:10,010 --> 00:38:11,990
In the future, we will become

720
00:38:12,020 --> 00:38:13,370
a laughingstock to others.

721
00:38:13,370 --> 00:38:15,450
Your Majesty, even if the war is urgent,

722
00:38:15,450 --> 00:38:16,810
a nation must uphold its laws.

723
00:38:16,810 --> 00:38:18,170
We must never cross that line.

724
00:38:18,170 --> 00:38:19,690
The Qilin Army was once a rebel force.

725
00:38:19,690 --> 00:38:21,010
If we rely on them too much,

726
00:38:21,010 --> 00:38:22,610
I'm afraid it will backfire.

727
00:38:22,690 --> 00:38:24,000
Yes, Your Majesty.

728
00:38:24,450 --> 00:38:28,150
Your Majesty must not use the Qilin Army.

729
00:38:34,010 --> 00:38:35,290
Shut up!

730
00:38:45,770 --> 00:38:47,880
Each and every one of you,

731
00:38:49,010 --> 00:38:50,810
if you're capable, then step up.

732
00:38:51,290 --> 00:38:53,650
What court rules are you talking about?

733
00:38:54,450 --> 00:38:56,970
Prime Minister Yue may be violating court rules,

734
00:38:56,970 --> 00:38:59,370
but he can lead troops to defeat the enemy.

735
00:39:00,010 --> 00:39:01,770
Anyone who keeps whining

736
00:39:02,290 --> 00:39:04,340
will be sent

737
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:07,620
to the battlefield as human shields.

738
00:39:18,170 --> 00:39:19,250
Tomorrow morning,

739
00:39:19,690 --> 00:39:20,860
Prime Minister Yue

740
00:39:21,090 --> 00:39:23,950
will lead the Qilin Army and Ning's troops

741
00:39:24,090 --> 00:39:25,350
on a joint expedition.

742
00:39:26,650 --> 00:39:28,530
I obey Your Majesty's order.
